headline: Kura Sushi: Southwest Slump Puts Pressure On Stock, But It's Still Expensive
summary: Kura Sushi faces significant challenges with cannibalization and operational deleveraging. Read why I reiterate my hold rating on KRUS stock, with a PT of $90.
